# ==============================================================================
# NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# Pull Request Labels Required for Sensitive Changes:
# - `golden-vector-change`: Any modification to golden vectors
# - `consensus-change`: Any change affecting consensus logic
# - `security-review`: Changes to security-critical code
# - `breaking-change`: API or protocol breaking changes
#
# Approval Process for Golden Vectors:
# 1. Create issue explaining why consensus is changing
# 2. Create PR with "golden-vector-change" label
# 3. Get code owner approval (@Quigles1337)
# 4. Get 2+ additional maintainer approvals
# 5. Security team sign-off
# 6. Update CHANGELOG.md with migration instructions
# 7. Increment version (golden vectors are versioned)
#
# Emergency Hotfixes:
# - Security vulnerabilities: Can bypass some reviews with incident commander approval
# - Must still get code owner approval for consensus-critical changes
# - Post-incident review required within 48 hours
#
